All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
## [1.90.19] - 2025-08-14
修复初始化时内存中没有默认通道配置导致定制失败的的问题

## [1.90.18] - 2025-08-12
修复深度还原后互联网定制失败的问题

## [1.90.17] - 2025-08-08
修复redfish创建用户报500及空定制config失败的问题

## [1.90.16] - 2025-08-05
bmc.kepler.IpmiService.ChannelNumberMappings接口名更新为bmc.kepler.IpmiService.ChannelNumberMapping
ExternalChannelNumber修改为External
InternalChannelNumber修改为Internal

## [1.90.15] - 2025-08-02
新增属性:MaxAccountLockoutThreshold、MaxAccountLockoutDuration、MaxHistoryPasswordCount
用来配置登录失败锁定次数和时间、历史密码的最大范围

## [1.90.14] - 2025-08-02
